---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. add tag as a commit's alias
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[caoj7@cncqcaoj7mbp1 basic]$git log -1
commit 8e4decce2a7edb4103603bae0f07140d330fdea6
Author: Jimmy Cao <jcao@gopivotal.com>
Date:   Fri Mar 28 16:34:40 2014 +0800

    some notes on git rollback and branch
[caoj7@cncqcaoj7mbp1 basic]$git tag stable-1 8e4decce2a7edb4103603bae0f07140d330fdea6
[caoj7@cncqcaoj7mbp1 basic]$git tag
stable-1
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2. add a annotated tag object
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[caoj7@cncqcaoj7mbp1 basic]$git tag -a annotated-stable-1 -m "learn to add a tag object with annotated-stable-1" 8e4decce2a7edb4103603bae0f07140d330fdea6
[caoj7@cncqcaoj7mbp1 basic]$git tag
annotated-stable-1
stable-1
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
3. delete a tag 
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[caoj7@cncqcaoj7mbp1 git-test]$git tag
annotated-stable-1
stable-1
[caoj7@cncqcaoj7mbp1 git-test]$git tag -d stable-1
Deleted tag 'stable-1' (was 8e4decc)
[caoj7@cncqcaoj7mbp1 git-test]$git tag
annotated-stable-1
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
4. review a tag
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[caoj7@cncqcaoj7mbp1 git-test]$git show annotated-stable-1
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
5. push a tag to a remote repo
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[caoj7@cncqcaoj7mbp1 git-test]$git push origin stable-1
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
6. push all new-added tags to repo
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[caoj7@cncqcaoj7mbp1 git-test]$git push origin stable-1
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
git push origin --tags
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
